-- Author      : Isaac Florez
-- Upgrade date: 25/08/2020
-- Description : * Rename function UFN_CALCULATE_DAILY_AVERAGE_CONSUMPTION to
--				   UFN_CALCULATE_DAILY_AVERAGE_CONSUMPTION_AND_FREQUENCY.
