-- Description:	Change the way of finish orders (Quarantine)
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Modified   : Oscar Hern叩n Londo単o Ospina
-- Modify Date: 19/05/2015 
-- Description:	Change @ovaPriority accuracy
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Author     : Julian Andres Gonzalez Velez
