-- Description : Use OS for @CreateFromAction when the Optimizer calls SP
--               GENERATE_REPLENISHMENT_SUGGESTIONS_HISTORY
-- Version     : 4.9.4
-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Author      : Oscar Londo単o
-- Upgrade date: 05/01/2018
